snippet.title: Digital Sketching of an Indie Game Character - For a Business Simulation Tycoon  Game - Devlog #1
snippet.description:
Time-lapse sketch of one of our characters. Say hello to Master Lee, who will be the business mentor in the upcoming indie tycoon business simulation game, Business Heroes: Food Truck Simulation, scheduled for Early Access on June 2024.
What do you guys think? Please comment below.

Give us a like and subscribe to our channel for further updates on our journey in making Business Heroes: Food Truck Simulation.

Our artist Xi Ding IG: @xidingart 
Music by David Hollandsworth twitter: @daveydad

See more game information at https://businessheroes.cool/ 
Our website: https://visionaries.me/
Join us on our active discord channel for further discussion and more information: https://discord.com/invite/HpDZM7v
Our twitter: https://twitter.com/We_Visionaries
Our Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/we_visionar...
